Author: coingirl87#6489
Content: @PTYX  how KOMODO will benefit from chainzilla and Chainzilla from KOMODO?

Author: PTYX#6840
Content: We will add value to Komodo by redesigning and peer reviewing all the apps. Seeking appstore approval after the redesigns. Also, we are in a constant search for companies and institutions that want to use blockchain but haven't been able to implement it. Every chain that ChainZilla adds to Komodo adds value to the DPoW layer. We will also become one of the first second-tier notarization layer on the platform to provide a different security options for different types of chains.

Author: PTYX#6840
Content: ChainZilla benefits from Komodo's open source tech. As we will benefit from QTum's and NEM's. The premier contracts that chainzilla is seeking plan to bring on the new types of projects to Komodo. Even though we offer different blockchain products we believe the best minimum viable blockchain can be created on Komodo. So that's what we will make our primary weapon.

Author: PTYX#6840
Content: ChainZilla is the business layer built on top of Komodo and othee open source tech
